        },
        "text_fRRw7g": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Best for:</strong> The daily driver and occasional tourer who wants a noticeable upgrade without going extreme.</p><ul><li><strong>Lift Height:</strong> 3 Inches</li><li><strong>Tyre Size:</strong> Engineered for either 35-inch or 37-inch tyres.</li><li><strong>Suspension Tech:</strong> Utilises a comprehensive <strong>BDS 3\" Kit</strong>, which includes a differential drop, sway bar relocation, and a rear block kit to dial in a perfectly level ride.</li><li><strong>Shock Configuration:</strong> <strong>Fox 2.5 Performance Series</strong> HTO<strong> Shocks</strong> <em>(front and rear)</em>. These provide excellent on-road comfort while resisting heat fade on harsh, corrugated roads.</li><li><strong>Extras:</strong> We also include colour-coded <strong>Husky Extenda Flares</strong> and <strong>ORI Metal mud flap brackets with rubber</strong> to ensure your vehicle is completely compliant and federally approved.</li><li><strong>What's Not Included:</strong> Just your wheels and tyres! All you need to do is pick your style. We have already set the specific wheel offsets required to keep the build federally compliant, so there is no need to stress about load ratings or legality.</li><li><strong>KIT Number: CHV-2500-STAGE-1-NB1</strong></li></ul>"
          }
