            "subheading": "Stage 2: $15,000* - Installed & Engineered"
          }
        },
        "heading_dHpa9y": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Stage 2: The Heavy Hitter 3\" Upgrade</strong>",
            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": false,
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_eiTTm6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Best for:</strong> The enthusiast who wants a massive improvement in suspension with complete adjustment for their vehicle's ride, featuring premium Fox 2.5 Performance Elite shocks.</p><ul><li><strong>Lift Height:</strong> 3 Inches</li><li><strong>Tyre Size:</strong> Engineered for either 35-inch or 37-inch tyres.</li><li><strong>Suspension Tech:</strong> Utilises a comprehensive <strong>BDS 3\" Kit</strong>, which includes a differential drop, sway bar relocation, and a rear block kit to dial in a perfectly level ride.</li><li><strong>Shock Configuration:</strong> <strong>Fox 2.5 Performance Elite Series Shocks</strong> <em>(front and rear)</em> featuring remote reservoirs and adjustable damping. You can literally dial in the ride with a simple clicker—soften it up for the highway, or firm it up for the tracks.</li><li><strong>Extras:</strong> We also include colour-coded <strong>Husky Extenda Flares</strong> and <strong>ORI Metal mud flap brackets with rubber</strong> to ensure your vehicle is completely compliant and federally approved.</li><li><strong>What's Not Included:</strong> Just your wheels and tyres! All you need to do is pick your style. We have already set the specific wheel offsets required to keep the build federally compliant, so there is no need to stress about load ratings or legality.</li><li><strong>CHV-2500-STAGE-2-NB1</strong></li></ul>"
          }
        }
