            "highlight_style": "none",
            "enable_highlight_text_color": false,
            "heading_size": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_Ktnecb": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>The undisputed King of the Off-Road. Front Coil-Over performance meets Kelderman 4-Link rear air suspension.</em></p><ul><li><strong>GVM Rating:</strong> 6000kg | <strong>GCM:</strong> 12,474kg</li><li><strong>Key Features:</strong> Fox 2.5 Performance Elite with BDS Lift Kit Technology (6.5-Inch Coil-Over Suspension Lift engineered for up to 37\" Tyres), featuring a <strong>Kelderman 4-Link full air rear suspension setup</strong>.</li><li><strong>Best For:</strong> The ultimate enthusiast who demands Super Tourer status without compromise.</li><li><strong>Benefit:</strong> This is the absolute pinnacle of suspension engineering. Combining the benefit of a BDS Coil-Over front end with the payload flexibility of a Kelderman 4-Link rear air setup, this package makes the ultimate dream a reality. 100% federally approved Pre-Rego, safe, insured, and ready to dominate any terrain in total luxury.</li><li><strong>Part Number:</strong> VEH-STAGE6-GVM-K<br/></li></ul><p></p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
